citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 11:40am-12:10pm
on 07-FEB-22. Inspectors left a voicemail at the listed phone and honked the horn from the driveway. No response was
received within 30 minutes of initial contact.
